headline: Exelon (EXC) Tops Q4 Earnings Estimates
summary: Exelon (EXC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +11.74% and -2.27%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
